<p>The secondary call-to-action pattern displays a heading, some introductory text, a call-to-action button and a background image.</p>

<h3>Rules for secondary call-to-action</h3>
<ul>
	<li>You must only use one secondary call-to-action per page.</li>
    <li>You may use a transparent overlay over the background by adding <code>transparent-overlay</code> to the secondary-call div.</li>
    <li>You must use at least one call-to-action button, but not more than three.</li>
</ul>

